---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About — Waldo Vanderhaeghen"
  description="PM, builder, and occasional thinker. Based in Berlin."
>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-photo">
        <img src="/images/waldo-profile.jpg" alt="Waldo Vanderhaeghen" width="280" height="280" />
      </div>

      <div class="about-bio">
        <h1>About</h1>

        <p>
          I'm Waldo — a product manager and builder based in Berlin. I spend most of my
          time thinking about AI tooling, building automations that solve real personal
          problems, and writing about what I learn along the way.
        </p>

        <p>
          My day job is PM work: specs, tickets, coordination, roadmaps. My side projects
          are where I close the gap between "I wonder if that's possible" and an answer.
          Most of what's on this site started as a thing I needed and couldn't find.
        </p>

        <p>
          I'm particularly interested in the gap between AI demos and AI that actually
          works in production — reliable categorization, deterministic pipelines, audit
          trails, things that keep running when you're not watching.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>

        <p>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/waldovander/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
          &nbsp;·&nbsp;
          <a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: var(--prose-width);
    margin: 3rem auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .about-photo { text-align: center; }
  }

  .about-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 220px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    display: block;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
